                    <span>I liked the book and all of the poetry in it, but all of the lustful poems confused me when tupac had a woman who was his potential wife.  I think Angela got played in a few ways.</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">Finished the book in about 3 hours</div>
                    <div>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Rating: </span>
                      <span>4</span>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Helpful: </span>
